  "detailed_description": "\"ElderGods Simulator\" blends auto chess with rogue-lite elements, putting you in the role of a resurrected dark god. Recruit followers and captives, combine and upgrade relics to enhance your power. Every playthrough is unique with randomly generated allies and enemies. Mix transcendent materials to create custom skills and build your legion.<br><br>Game Features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlimited Followers and Enemies: </h2>Support massive battles with no cap on the number of units, making every fight an epic clash.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Built-in idle mode, making work time more enjoyable</h2>The idle mode is stitched in, allowing you to collect treasures in the background while busy. Essential for those who like to slack off at work.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Experience Every Time: </h2>With randomly generated followers and enemies, no two games are the same.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable Relics: </h2>Use transcendent materials to upgrade relics and create your own unique skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embrace the chaos, strategize your moves, and build an unstoppable legion in \"ElderGods Simulator.\"<br> Ready to command your army?",
  "about_the_game": "\"ElderGods Simulator\" blends auto chess with rogue-lite elements, putting you in the role of a resurrected dark god. Recruit followers and captives, combine and upgrade relics to enhance your power. Every playthrough is unique with randomly generated allies and enemies. Mix transcendent materials to create custom skills and build your legion.<br><br>Game Features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlimited Followers and Enemies: </h2>Support massive battles with no cap on the number of units, making every fight an epic clash.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/757216dc554e57363a4a1eccd6d98af8.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/73f9d91d8db25a6ea66c8853018a7a25.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Built-in idle mode, making work time more enjoyable</h2>The idle mode is stitched in, allowing you to collect treasures in the background while busy. Essential for those who like to slack off at work.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/6197f581e0d149d6d490e8f3f1892b2d.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Experience Every Time: </h2>With randomly generated followers and enemies, no two games are the same.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/3e28b650c68bb9576385878790c92e52.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable Relics: </h2>Use transcendent materials to upgrade relics and create your own unique skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.poster.avif?t=1721389605\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.webm?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808320/extras/447daab6164811cc9b5de17827a4384f.mp4?t=1721389605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embrace the chaos, strategize your moves, and build an unstoppable legion in \"ElderGods Simulator.\"<br> Ready to command your army?",
